  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink98-kilavi">puṟattoḻukkam uḷatākiya tuṇaiyāṉē pulantu vāyil nērāt talaimakaḷ koṭumai
          talaimakaṉ kūṟak kēṭṭa tōḻi avaṟkuc colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink98">
          <l>taṇpuṉa lāṭun taṭaṅkōṭ ṭerumai</l>
          <l>tiṇpiṇi yampiyiṟ ṟōṉṟu mūra</l>
          <l>voṇṭoṭi maṭamaka ḷivaḷiṉu</l>
          <l>nuntaiyum yāyuṅ kaṭiyarō niṉṉē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">


          <l> O man from a village </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> where the broad-horned buffalo that bathes in the cool flood </l>
          <l rend="indent4"> appears like a firmly tied little boat! </l>
          <l> Will your father and my mother be more of a protection [against] you </l>
          <l> than this innocent girl with the bright bracelets? / </l>
          <l> Will your father and my mother chide/denounce you more </l>
          <l> than this innocent girl with the bright bracelets? </l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
